<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/core/libs.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/hope-ui.min.css?v=2.0.0" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #f39c12;
            --secondary-color: #004e92;
            --accent-color: #00b4db;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #002147, #004e92, #00b4db, #f39c12);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background: #002147;
        }

        .hero-section {
            height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradient 15s ease infinite;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
        }

        @keyframes gradient {
            0% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }

            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
        }

        .hero-content {
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn-ishraq {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-ishraq:hover {
            background-color: var(--accent-color);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: white;
        }

        .logo-container svg {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
        }

        .footer-landing {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .contact-info b {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .hero-content p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .footer-landing {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" stroke="#f39c12" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="10 5" />
                    <path
                        d="M50 20V30M50 70V80M20 50H30M70 50H80M28.8 28.8L35.9 35.9M64.1 64.1L71.2 71.2M28.8 71.2L35.9 64.1M64.1 28.8L71.2 35.9"
                        stroke="#f39c12" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" />
                    <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="15" fill="#f39c12">
                        <animate attributeName="r" values="13;17;13" dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                    </circle>
                    <path d="M50 40C55 40 60 45 60 50C60 55 55 60 50 60C45 60 40 55 40 50C40 45 45 40 50 40Z"
                        fill="white" opacity="0.3" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>إشراق</h1>
            <p>يداً بيد لإعادة النور والكهرباء لغزة .. شريككم الموثوق في رحلة إعمار قطاع غزة</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-ishraq">تسجيل الدخول للنظام</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-landing">
            <div>
                ©
                <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> <b>إشراق</b> - مشروع إدارة المولدات والكهرباء
                في قطاع غزة
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
                تطوير: المهندس <b>باسل ابو سليم</b> | هاتف: 0592428779 | بريد: basilsaleem11@gmail.com
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/assets/js/core/libs.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/assets/js/hope-ui.js"></script>
</body>

</html>